{"product_id":"vielo-organic-facial-masque-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Facial Masque 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePurifying organic mask to gently yet effectively cleanse, soothe and hydrate the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade with organic whey (nourishing), white clay (purifying), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic witch hazel water (nurturing), organic rosehip seed oil (soothing), and organic extracts of calendula (regenerating), cucumber (refreshing) and mallow (protecting).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply a generous layer to clean face and neck. Leave for 15 minutes until dry. Rinse gently with warm water. Use once or twice a week.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Hamamelis Virginiana Water**, Rosa Canina Fruit Oil**, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate*, Cetyl Alcohol*, Glycerin**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Aqua*, Kaolin*, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter**, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil**, Oenothera Biennis Oil**, Sodium Levulinate*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Citric Acid*, Xanthan Gum*, Sodium Anisate, Tocopherol*, Potassium Sorbate, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Cucumis Sativus Fruit Extract**, Malva Sylvestris Flower Extract**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract**, Sodium Lactate*.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (81,7%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901095088455,"sku":null,"price":40.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-facial-masque-50ml-901935.jpg?v=1739897176","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/vielo-organic-facial-masque-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}